{"tid":1576810,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港鐵喺倫敦投資嘅地鐵新支線Elizabeth Line 係可以獲得14億英鎊!!係14億英鎊!!","createTime":"2019-09-17T11:42:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T09:38:17.000Z","uid":42751,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"272bda1843002c16a9d0efe40c6f670e85e3b606","tid":1576810,"uid":42751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T11:42:11.000Z","msg":"原來港鐵喺倫敦投資嘅地鐵新支線Elizabeth Line 係可以獲得14億英鎊!!係14億英鎊!! <br />\n我地而家要簽呢個Petition，令到倫敦市長知道，港鐵係唔識得管理，應該再審視係咪應該俾港鐵喺倫敦繼續營運落去！<br />\n<br />\n港鐵已唔係一間奉行資本主義、以股東利益為依歸嘅上市公司。其惡行如下：<br />\n1.聽從警方指示喺八三一晚起關閉太子站多達30小時， 喺發生多人受傷情況下竟唔俾記者進入採訪及不准救護員入內，並暫停該站的列車服務。而其實警方無權要求港鐵關站關站，港鐵無義務聽從警方要求關站！<br />\n2港鐵多次喺示威開始前、毫無危險的時候，暫停示威地區的列車服務（例如觀塘區大遊行當日12：30就已經關閉觀塘綫的幾個站），而唔係好似以前一樣不理政治因素而照常提供服務。<br />\n以上不止令港鐵車費收入減少，仲會損害到廣大市民嘅利益。<br />\n呢啲都顯示港鐵已唔係服務股東的上市公司！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/sadiq-khan-transport-for-london-terminate-mtr-crossrails-s-1-4bn-contract-to-operate-crossrail-elizabeth-line-saynotomtrcrossrail?recruiter=229101546&amp;recruited_by_id=61dbb070-b1d7-11e4-8592-cbd20ac04e4b&amp;utm_source=share_petition&amp;utm_medium=copylink&amp;utm_campaign=petition_dashboard\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fsadiq-khan-transport-for-london-terminate-mtr-crossrails-s-1-4bn-contract-to-operate-crossrail-elizabeth-line-saynotomtrcrossrail%3Frecruiter%3D229101546%26recruited_by_id%3D61dbb070-b1d7-11e4-8592-cbd20ac04e4b%26utm_source%3Dshare_petition%26utm_medium%3Dcopylink%26utm_campaign%3Dpetition_dashboard&d=ZtzEMfLxU%2BwdrFVc2rz1%2F7PGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=87cf1e02\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/sadiq-khan-transport-for-london-terminate-mtr-crossrails-s-1-4bn-contract-to-operate-crossrail-elizabeth-line-saynotomtrcrossrail?recruiter=229101546&amp;recruited_by_id=61dbb070-b1d7-11e4-8592-cbd20ac04e4b&amp;utm_source=share_petition&amp;utm_medium=copylink&amp;utm_campaign=petition_dashboard</a>"},{"pid":"9a90f86d394c0905